    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive at all costs!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387480/extras/5e1c2a4bee2b86b230f3ecd1c942d71f.poster.avif?t=1733941064\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387480/extras/5e1c2a4bee2b86b230f3ecd1c942d71f.webm?t=1733941064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387480/extras/5e1c2a4bee2b86b230f3ecd1c942d71f.mp4?t=1733941064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SOMEWHERE</strong> takes you to a brutal and mysterious world where survival is your ultimate challenge. Stranded on the wild island of Esterhall without weapons, food, or shelter, can you endure?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Intense Survival:</strong> Manage hunger, thirst, and cold.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Crafting Mastery:</strong> Build tools, weapons, and shelters from resources.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Exploration:</strong> Discover mysterious locations and uncover the secrets of a vanished civilization.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Multiplayer:</strong> Team up with others or compete for rare resources.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Immersive Atmosphere:</strong> Realistic nature, dynamic weather, and a gripping story.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your limits in this harsh world! Can you survive where nature reigns supreme?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your survival journey today!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SOMEWHERE — your challenge, your island, your story!</strong></p>",
